# Page Migration

When editing pages, auth, header, or footer: replace raw HTML with LD components per `agent-context/page-migration.md`.

## Replace before finishing

- `<input>` → `TextField` (pass `textFieldProps` for id, name, autoComplete)
- `<textarea>` → `TextArea`
- `<button>` → `Button` or `IconButton`
- External `<a href>` → LD `Link`
- `lucide-react` → `@/app/components/Icons/Icons`

## After editing

1. Update status row in `agent-context/page-migration.md`
2. Run `pnpm run build`
